        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7095",
        "content": "Darwinism, which at first was declared by the clergy to be brutal, degrading, atheistic, and anti Christian, is now included as part of the Bible teaching.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
