        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7095",
        "content": "In a similar manner, the Copernican theory, the theory of gravitation, the nebular hypothesis, the theory of uniformity in geology, and every scientific advance has been opposed on the same grounds; that is, that these are against the teachings of the Christian Church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
