        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7095",
        "content": "There have been futile experiments without number; highly successful achievements have been thrown aside; one type of life after another has arisen and has pushed up a blind alley to extinction.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
